ootball/barcelona/2019/12/03/5de6d4efca4741ba6b8b45c2.html</ref>\n\n'''Decorations'''\n*[[Royal Order of Sports Merit|Gold Medal of the Royal Order of Sporting Merit]]: 2011<ref>{{cite news |title=Las campeones del mundo de f\u00fatbol ya tienen la Real Orden del M\u00e9rito Deportivo |url=http://www.mundodeportivo.com/20111005/futbol/seleccion-espanola/las-campeones-del-mundo-de-futbol-ya-tienen-la-real-orden-del-merito-deportivo_54226408413.html |language=Spanish |newspaper=Mundo Deportivo |date=5 October 2011}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n*[https://www.fcbarcelona.com/en/football/first-team/players/2737/gerard-pique Profile] at the FC Barcelona website\n*{{BDFutbol}}\n*[http://www.bdfutbol.com/en/p/j944.html?cat=SEL National team data] at BDFutbol\n*{{Soccerway}}\n*[http://www.stretfordend.co.uk/playermenu/pique.html Gerard Piqu\u00e9 profile] StretfordEnd.co.uk\n*{{NFT player}}\n*{{FIFA player}}\n*{{UEFA player}}\n\n{{FC Barcelona squad}}\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Spain squads\n| bg = #C60B1E\n| fg = #FBEA0E\n| bordercolor = #000033\n| list1 = \n{{Spain squad 2009 FIFA Confederations Cup}}\n{{Spain squad 2010 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Spain squad UEFA Euro 2012}}\n{{Spain squad 2013 FIFA Confederations Cup}}\n{{Spain squad 2014 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Spain squad UEFA Euro 2016}}\n{{Spain squad 2018 FIFA World Cup}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Awards\n| bg = gold\n| fg = navy\n| list1 = \n{{La Liga Defender of the Year}}\n{{UEFA Euro 2012 Team of the Tournament}}\n{{2014\u201315 La Liga Team of the Year}}\n{{2015\u201316 La Liga Team of the Year}}\n{{2010 UEFA Team of the Year}}\n{{2011 UEFA Team of the Year}}\n{{2012 UEFA Team of the Year}}\n{{2015 UEFA Team of the Year}}\n{{2016 UEFA Team of the Year}}\n}}\n{{Shakira}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pique, Gerard}}\n[[Category:1987 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Barcelona]]\n[[Category:Spanish footballers]]\n[[Category:Catalan 